ckquote><br />\n依下驚bo 佢係不停委任校董到夠人就擺免佢 遲下邊個校長唔聽話都可以用依種方法擺免佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b9507e2f1fb6f72912eb565262d7dfb1427896","tid":364270,"uid":39628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"病假餅卡 + 散水餅<br />\n班老師記得追返呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00df1b5352d3460634da84fc201032e098d683c6","tid":364270,"uid":134683,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去第2間學校再做??</blockquote><br />\n教育局會取消佢校長資格<br />\n最多剩番個教師牌<br />\n但佢違反專業守則<br />\n又有機會判刑事<br />\n所以教師牌被吊銷係遲早既事"},{"pid":"7a47893bc8613988ba5c89c7b986162a8d719bb2","tid":364270,"uid":17776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:20:53.000Z","msg":"咁慘係咪要借餅消愁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df910b0f7b8a54aa0504d6ffb2a8855e917e79cd","tid":364270,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知教局可以委任幾多校董???</blockquote><br />\n依下驚bo 佢係不停委任校董到夠人就擺免佢 遲下邊個校長唔聽話都可以用依種方法擺免佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢下冇得唔咁做<br />\n不過要加校董要跟返正常程序<br />\n只能希望程序冇俾人濫用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8639c0c7e04411817e9e7936b683e94684845d7","tid":364270,"uid":137717,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"點解咁既人都做到校長？<br />\n但我就係拎得幾萬蚊個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj